- Zero-yaml support is current; YAML support ends 2025
- The migration tool (`npx nango migrate-to-zero-yaml`) has known issues
- Manual migration following these patterns is more reliable
- Delete `nango.yaml` completely - its presence blocks zero-yaml mode
